body:
What with all the awesome electronic music coming out of Australia over the course of the past couple of years (we’re talking Klo, Autumn, Tora etc.

), it was only a matter of time before one of the acts really nailed it, and Aussie duo **Yuma X** (Lucy & Jake) have done just that, on their debut _Swimming Pool_. A rework/cover of a track originally released back in 2008, it’s delicate and lovelorn, all underpinned by some solid production. Check it out below.

Follow our [Spotify On Repeat playlist](https://open.spotify.com/user/crackintheroad/playlist/1UB6gJIZpmiO0H2zmSbg02) for a selection of the current hottest tracks.
